Title: Detective Conan: The Fourteenth Target
Writer: Gosho Aoyama (manga), Toyohiko Okuyama (original story), Mitomu Asai (original story), Kazunari Furuuchi (screenplay), Jeremy Carlile (head writer), Mike McFarland (script writer)
Actors: Laura Bailey, Troy Baker, Bob Carter, Chafûrin
Plot: People who were linked with Mori Kogoro are being attacked or killed according to their names' number sequences.
